     =========================================================
     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                Example for divisions History file
                ----------------------------------
This file should be used by the G4 example coordinator to briefly
summarize all major modifications introduced in the code and keep
track of all tags.

     ----------------------------------------------------------
     * Reverse chronological order (last date on top), please *
     ----------------------------------------------------------

18-08-21 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Removed no longer necessary custom physics-list; use default FTFP_BERT.
- Removed custome SteppingVerbose class, use default G4SteppingVerboseWithUnits.
- Removed custom settings for visualisation.
- Migrated to use G4RunManagerFactory.
- Switch off additional Navigation tests when running in MT mode.

22-03-17 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Updated physics-list to properly use particle-table iterator.

13-05-16 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Updated visualization/UI setup.

09-09-15 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Migrated to multi-threading.

22-03-13 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Fixed compilation warnings for variable shadowing...

05-12-12 J.Allison
----------------
- Migrated to DrawTrajectory (i_mode argument no longer available).

16-06-10 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Migrated physics-list to use particle-based multiple-scattering processes.

18-05-07 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Removed G4GAGTree from vis-manager, no longer existing.

08-06-06 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Use CLHEP namespace wherever necessary.

09-11-05 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Migrated to <sstream> from deprecated <strstream>.

06-06-05 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Fixed trivial compilation errors when using CLHEP 1.9 series.

12-05-04 G.Cosmo
----------------
- Added support for reflections (courtesy of I.Hrivnacova), new input
  argument for selection normal/reflected.

17-10-03 P.Arce (exdivisions-V05-02-00)
---------------
- Created.
